[
  {
    "text": "Hello, App Store developers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Greg from the App Store Review team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=2"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today we're going to share some best practices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=4"
  },
  {
    "text": "for creating great apps that do more for users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=6"
  },
  {
    "text": "while collecting less of their data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "At Apple, we believe that privacy ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "is a fundamental human right ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=14"
  },
  {
    "text": "and Apple products are designed to protect privacy ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "and give users control over their information. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "In addition to designing our products ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "with privacy protections, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=24"
  },
  {
    "text": "privacy is central in the App Store Review Guidelines. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "Guideline 5.1.1 in particular details some requirements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=29"
  },
  {
    "text": "that are essential for protecting users' information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Apple ecosystem. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "Improving your app's privacy practices won't only help you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "prevent issues in review, though. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "Users prefer apps that respect their privacy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "So today we're going to share three tips that will help you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=46"
  },
  {
    "text": "build great apps that put users in control of their data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=49"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our first tip: where possible, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "delay sign-in flows or remove them altogether. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, limit the data your app requests ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "to only what is necessary. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "And last, be ready with an alternative ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=65"
  },
  {
    "text": "when users decline to share their data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=67"
  },
  {
    "text": "Along the way, we'll share concrete examples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=70"
  },
  {
    "text": "that'll help you get started. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "So let's start with signing in. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "Wherever possible, let users enjoy your app without it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "People prefer to go without accounts where possible. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "They want to get to the action quickly, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=85"
  },
  {
    "text": "and forcing people to sign in ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "before they can do anything useful can be discouraging. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=88"
  },
  {
    "text": "To keep users engaged, let them explore your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=93"
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't include a login if there's no need for an account ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "or delay the login until the app's account-based features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=100"
  },
  {
    "text": "come into play. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=103"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, a sporting goods app might allow the public ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "to freely browse their products ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "until a user wants to purchase an item. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "This allows users to enjoy the app without sharing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "personal data until there's a specific need for it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=115"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our second tip is limit the data you request ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=120"
  },
  {
    "text": "to just what your app needs. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=123"
  },
  {
    "text": "Data minimization is a pillar of Apple's approach to privacy, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=126"
  },
  {
    "text": "and we encourage app developers like you to adopt it as well. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=129"
  },
  {
    "text": "Ask yourself, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=133"
  },
  {
    "text": "what features do I want to deliver to my app's users? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=134"
  },
  {
    "text": "And then, what's the minimum amount of data I need ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=137"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make this feature great? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "By asking yourself these questions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=144"
  },
  {
    "text": "early in your development process, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=146"
  },
  {
    "text": "you won't end up asking users for data you don't need. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see what this can look like for users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=152"
  },
  {
    "text": "in registration flows when apps try to access ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "a protected resource. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=156"
  },
  {
    "text": "In registration flows, we talked about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "when it makes sense to ask new users to register. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, consider what data you ask for in the registration flow. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "Information you request should be essential ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=170"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your app to function, or else, required by law. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "So let's look at an app that's asking for more than they need. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here we have a registration page for a shopping app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "Looks like all fields are required. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=182"
  },
  {
    "text": "Requiring the address makes sense since they'll need it ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "to send me my orders, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "but why would they need to know my birthday ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=188"
  },
  {
    "text": "or whether I'm married or not? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=191"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, it turns out this app has a feature ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "that sends coupons to users on their birthday. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "While the coupons might be a nice perk, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=199"
  },
  {
    "text": "people can still enjoy the main shopping functionality ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "without the app knowing when they were born. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "But there are no features tied to marital status, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that should be removed altogether. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "And since knowing a user's date of birth ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "isn't essential for the app to function, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "it shouldn't require all new users to provide it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "Instead, this should be a clearly labeled optional field. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=220"
  },
  {
    "text": "Including a brief, transparent description ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "of how the birth date will be used ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "will also help people make an informed choice. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=229"
  },
  {
    "text": "Similarly, be careful when requesting ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "sensitive personal data like health and financial information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=235"
  },
  {
    "text": "or national ID numbers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "Only relevant app types ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a critical or legal need for this information, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "like medical or banking apps, should ask for it ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "with a clear explanation of how the data will be used ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=248"
  },
  {
    "text": "and stored. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=251"
  },
  {
    "text": "After reviewing your app's needs, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=253"
  },
  {
    "text": "you might find that your app actually doesn't need ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "much data from users to authenticate their account. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=257"
  },
  {
    "text": "In that case, instead of a long registration process, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=261"
  },
  {
    "text": "consider offering Sign in with Apple ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=265"
  },
  {
    "text": "as a privacy-focused alternative. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=266"
  },
  {
    "text": "With Sign in with Apple, users spend less time ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=269"
  },
  {
    "text": "filling out forms or registering emails ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "and can quickly start enjoying what your app has to offer. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "In addition to registration, many apps use device resources ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=279"
  },
  {
    "text": "which are protected by default on Apple operating systems. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "This means if you want to do things like use the microphone, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=286"
  },
  {
    "text": "communicate with Bluetooth devices, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=289"
  },
  {
    "text": "or use location services, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=291"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll need to ask for the user's permission first. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=293"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our recommendation here is the same: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=296"
  },
  {
    "text": "only ask for what you need. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "This advice applies to all protected resources ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=301"
  },
  {
    "text": "on Apple devices. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here are some more examples. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=305"
  },
  {
    "text": "Many apps offer an option to select a photo ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=308"
  },
  {
    "text": "for a profile page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "But if this is your app's only use for Photos, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "you don't need to request access ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=315"
  },
  {
    "text": "to every photo the user has ever taken. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=316"
  },
  {
    "text": "Instead, a better fit for your app's needs is photo picker, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": "so users can quickly select the perfect photo ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=323"
  },
  {
    "text": "for their profile without providing more access ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "than is required. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=328"
  },
  {
    "text": "Photo picker can also be configured ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=330"
  },
  {
    "text": "for selecting multiple photos or capturing photos and video.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=332"
  },
  {
    "text": "You may have a chat messaging app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=338"
  },
  {
    "text": "and are thinking about requesting access to Contacts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=340"
  },
  {
    "text": "to help people connect with their friends. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=342"
  },
  {
    "text": "We have another idea for you. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "Similar to photo picker, you can configure ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=349"
  },
  {
    "text": "a view controller for selecting contacts, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=351"
  },
  {
    "text": "letting users select the one or more contacts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "they'd like to connect with. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=356"
  },
  {
    "text": "For some apps, only a few features rely on location data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=359"
  },
  {
    "text": "Rather than prompting the location permission request ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=363"
  },
  {
    "text": "at launch, consider adding a Share Current Location button ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=365"
  },
  {
    "text": "right in your app's experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=369"
  },
  {
    "text": "When people tap the button, your app will receive access ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=372"
  },
  {
    "text": "to their location for that session, just like Allow Once, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=375"
  },
  {
    "text": "and will last until they leave the app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=378"
  },
  {
    "text": "This gives people a low-commitment option ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=381"
  },
  {
    "text": "when they use your app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "Like other protected resources, data in the Health app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=387"
  },
  {
    "text": "can be accessed with the user's permission through HealthKit. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=390"
  },
  {
    "text": "The Health app contains sensitive, personal information ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=394"
  },
  {
    "text": "and your app should have an appropriate reason ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=397"
  },
  {
    "text": "for trying to access this data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "If your app doesn't have any health or fitness features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=403"
  },
  {
    "text": "that would require this data, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=405"
  },
  {
    "text": "make sure your app doesn't include the HealthKit framework ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=407"
  },
  {
    "text": "or any references to it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=410"
  },
  {
    "text": "Otherwise, your app may not pass review. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=412"
  },
  {
    "text": "And don't forget most permission requests ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=416"
  },
  {
    "text": "include a purpose string. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=418"
  },
  {
    "text": "Purpose strings are short messages provided by you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=420"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your app's info p-list ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=423"
  },
  {
    "text": "describing how your app will use the requested data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=424"
  },
  {
    "text": "Writing clear purpose strings helps users ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "make informed decisions. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=431"
  },
  {
    "text": "For more tips on writing purpose strings, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=433"
  },
  {
    "text": "check out the links associated with this video.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "The main takeaway here is to think critically ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=441"
  },
  {
    "text": "about what data your app really needs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=443"
  },
  {
    "text": "and, wherever you can, build apps that require less. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=445"
  },
  {
    "text": "This leads us to our third tip: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=450"
  },
  {
    "text": "get creative with alternatives that still provide ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=453"
  },
  {
    "text": "great experiences when users decline to share their data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=456"
  },
  {
    "text": "People expect apps to still function ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=462"
  },
  {
    "text": "when they decide not to share their data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=464"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apps that don't create a poor user experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=468"
  },
  {
    "text": "and may not pass review. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=471"
  },
  {
    "text": "Anticipate that some users will decline ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=475"
  },
  {
    "text": "to have their data collected. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=478"
  },
  {
    "text": "Others may be using devices with parental controls activated ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=480"
  },
  {
    "text": "or other restricted privacy settings ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=484"
  },
  {
    "text": "limiting access to certain resources; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "be ready with an alternative. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=489"
  },
  {
    "text": "If someone prefers not to share their location data, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=493"
  },
  {
    "text": "let them manually input an address or postal code instead. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=497"
  },
  {
    "text": "When people would rather not take a photo of themselves, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=503"
  },
  {
    "text": "some apps let users customize an avatar, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=507"
  },
  {
    "text": "giving their profiles a personalized touch ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=509"
  },
  {
    "text": "without sharing more data than they need to. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=511"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, keep in mind, if the user decides ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=515"
  },
  {
    "text": "to not grant permission to access a protected resource, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=518"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's important to respect their decision. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=521"
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't include messages in your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=524"
  },
  {
    "text": "asking them to change their mind. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "If they try to use a feature that requires access ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=529"
  },
  {
    "text": "to a protected resource, though, it can be appropriate ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=532"
  },
  {
    "text": "to include a message letting them know ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=535"
  },
  {
    "text": "they can change their permission choices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Settings app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=539"
  },
  {
    "text": "Those are our tips for doing more with less data. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=542"
  },
  {
    "text": "Incorporating these practices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=545"
  },
  {
    "text": "early in your development process will not only help you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=547"
  },
  {
    "text": "avoid delays in review, your users will appreciate ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=549"
  },
  {
    "text": "the steps you've taken to respect their privacy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=552"
  },
  {
    "text": "We think these privacy best practices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=556"
  },
  {
    "text": "will help your app collect less ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=558"
  },
  {
    "text": "while delivering a satisfying, feature-rich experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=559"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for watching our video. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=565"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're interested in learning more about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=567"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple's approach to privacy and other best practices, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=568"
  },
  {
    "text": "check out the other videos ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=571"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the Apple Developer website and app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110352/?time=572"
  }
]